----------------Welcome to North Brookfield, Massachusetts----------------

Months before the dawn of the War of 1812,  the small town of North Brookfield, Massachusetts was founded in the Northern Parish of Brookfield county. With a history stretching well over two hundreds years, the little-known Massachusetts town hosted many of America's greatest successfuls, such as George M.
